## 🔑 Environment Variables to Add to `.env.local`

```env
# Meta / Instagram
META_APP_ID=your_app_id
META_APP_SECRET=your_app_secret
INSTAGRAM_USER_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_long_lived_token
INSTAGRAM_BUSINESS_ACCOUNT_ID=your_ig_business_id

# LinkedIn
LINKEDIN_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_oauth_token
LINKEDIN_ORGANIZATION_URN=urn:li:organization:YOUR_ORG_ID

# Google Analytics 4
GA4_PROPERTY_ID=properties/YOUR_PROPERTY_ID
GOOGLE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_EMAIL=your-sa@project.iam.gserviceaccount.com
GOOGLE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_PRIVATE_KEY="-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----\n..."
```

---

## 🔄 How Data Will Flow (n8n Sync)

```
n8n Scheduled Trigger (daily @ 2 AM IST)
  ├── Call Meta Graph API → fetch yesterday's post insights
  ├── Call LinkedIn API   → fetch page + post stats
  ├── Call GA4 API        → fetch website metrics
  └── INSERT all rows → Supabase social_analytics
                              ↓
               Dashboard auto-refreshes → real charts
```

> [!NOTE]
> The n8n workflow for pulling analytics can be built after the designer integration is complete.
